  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hi everyone! This is a casual puzzle game that simulates a claw machine.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game, you can experience a relaxing time. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Move the joystick to press the button and collect the plush toys!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2941350/extras/6f266800ceba98c160f73a76b95a5f2f.poster.avif?t=1768036693\" width=480 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2941350/extras/6f266800ceba98c160f73a76b95a5f2f.webm?t=1768036693\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2941350/extras/6f266800ceba98c160f73a76b95a5f2f.mp4?t=1768036693\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>The first 15 are fixed rewards in the level, the remaining need to be obtained through random catch in free mode</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The acquired dolls can be viewed on the collection shelf. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are a total of 10 levels, with a total of 30 cute dolls of the same style waiting for you to acquire!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2941350/extras/cd10712fe33874adc8782826dc94d155.poster.avif?t=1768036693\" width=480 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2941350/extras/cd10712fe33874adc8782826dc94d155.webm?t=1768036693\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2941350/extras/cd10712fe33874adc8782826dc94d155.mp4?t=1768036693\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Operation guide/manual</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Move the grabbing claw by using the buttons or joysticks on the machine.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Position and adjust to move the claw to a suitable position so that it can clamp the target object when grabbing it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When the claw is in the ideal position, press the button, and the claw will descend and try to clamp the target object.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once the target object is clamped, the claw will start to rise, bringing the object out of the claw machine to get the doll.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2941350/extras/d0496207c94a938ef4645201f08775f3.poster.avif?t=1768036693\" width=480 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2941350/extras/d0496207c94a938ef4645201f08775f3.webm?t=1768036693\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2941350/extras/d0496207c94a938ef4645201f08775f3.mp4?t=1768036693\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game difficulty is casual level, which is suitable for players who do not want to spend too much effort to pass the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I hope everyone will like this game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After clearing customs, you can experience various exquisite character illustrations as a reward.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hi everyone! This is a casual puzzle game that simulates a claw machine.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game, you can experience a relaxing time. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Move the joystick to press the button and collect the plush toys!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2941350/extras/6f266800ceba98c160f73a76b95a5f2f.poster.avif?t=1768036693\" width=480 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2941350/extras/6f266800ceba98c160f73a76b95a5f2f.webm?t=1768036693\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2941350/extras/6f266800ceba98c160f73a76b95a5f2f.mp4?t=1768036693\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>The first 15 are fixed rewards in the level, the remaining need to be obtained through random catch in free mode</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The acquired dolls can be viewed on the collection shelf. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are a total of 10 levels, with a total of 30 cute dolls of the same style waiting for you to acquire!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2941350/extras/cd10712fe33874adc8782826dc94d155.poster.avif?t=1768036693\" width=480 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2941350/extras/cd10712fe33874adc8782826dc94d155.webm?t=1768036693\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2941350/extras/cd10712fe33874adc8782826dc94d155.mp4?t=1768036693\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Operation guide/manual</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Move the grabbing claw by using the buttons or joysticks on the machine.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Position and adjust to move the claw to a suitable position so that it can clamp the target object when grabbing it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When the claw is in the ideal position, press the button, and the claw will descend and try to clamp the target object.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once the target object is clamped, the claw will start to rise, bringing the object out of the claw machine to get the doll.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2941350/extras/d0496207c94a938ef4645201f08775f3.poster.avif?t=1768036693\" width=480 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2941350/extras/d0496207c94a938ef4645201f08775f3.webm?t=1768036693\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2941350/extras/d0496207c94a938ef4645201f08775f3.mp4?t=1768036693\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game difficulty is casual level, which is suitable for players who do not want to spend too much effort to pass the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I hope everyone will like this game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After clearing customs, you can experience various exquisite character illustrations as a reward.</p>",
